<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_0ccd54b5b58a.aspx"><b>临安春雨初霁</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e9%99%86%e6%b8%b8">陆游</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson0ccd54b5b58a">
<p>世味年来薄似纱，谁令骑马客京华。<br />小楼一夜听春雨，深巷明朝卖杏花。<br />矮纸斜行闲作草，晴窗细乳戏分茶。<br />素衣莫起风尘叹，犹及清明可到家。</p>
